==试图在2011年大选竞选失败==
2011年大选，黄德祥领导的一组无党籍人士，因为呈交提名表格迟了35秒，结果被取消资格，无法与人民行动党队竞选丹戎巴葛集选区。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/GeneralElection/News/Story/STIStory_662123.html|title=Singapore heads to history-making polls on May 7|last=Chua|first=Lee Hoong|date=28 April 2011|work=Straits Times|accessdate=9 May 2011|archive-date=2011-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808154738/http://www.straitstimes.com/GeneralElection/News/Story/STIStory_662123.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

